\nmSUSY> 2 TeV values and for all the mixings considered. We show that all the\nthree channels could be measurable at the LHC even in these heavy SUSY\nscenarios, being h -> tau mu the most promising one, with up to about hundred\nof events expected with the current LHC centre-of-mass energy and luminosity.\nThe most promising predictions for the future LHC stage are also included.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2013 18:31:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-18"}
