lands are rapidly swallowed up by the\nionizing background, this characteristic scale does not change much as the\nreionization proceeds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2013 21:00:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-01-17"}
