s around BHs. We find that the physical\nconditions in these disks may be conducive to planet formation, hence leading\nto the possible existence of planets orbiting black holes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2013 21:31:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
